## Installation

```bash
pip install flareui
```

## Quick Start

```python
from flareui.core.component import Component

class Counter(Component):
    def __init__(self):
        super().__init__()
        self._state = {"count": 0}
    
    def template(self):
        return """
        <div>
            <h1>Count: {{ self._state['count'] }}</h1>
            <button @click="self.increment()">Increment</button>
        </div>
        """
    
    def increment(self):
        self.set_state({"count": self._state["count"] + 1})
```

